<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
   <head>
      <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
   </head>
   <body>
      <h1>New watch was created by <%= @watch.from_user.vname %></h1>
      <p>Congratulations friend for achieving a new watcher, you must
         feel very proud of this accomplishment. Guess they must
         really like your content quite a lot to follow an up and
         coming star such as yourself.
      </p>
      <p>Your new watcher is currently watching <%= @watch.watchtype.name %>.</p>
      <p>In recognition of your various talents here on Duelingpets.net, we
         the staff have decided to award you <%= @points %> points. We hope
         that you can put these points to good use. We hope you can continue
         to provide fun and entertaining content for all of us here to enjoy.
         Keep up the good work.
      </p>
      <br>
      <p>The Duelingpets Staff Team</p>
   </body>
</html>
